Title: Multiple-dose pharmacokinetics confirm no accumulation and dose proportionality of the novel promotile drug tegaserod (HTF 919).
Name: Tegaserod

Parameter: area under the plasma concentration-time curve over one dosing interval (tau, 0-12 h after drug administration, AUC tau)
Sentece: Mean measured maximum plasma concentration after multiple administrations (Cmax,ss) and area under the plasma concentration-time curve over one dosing interval (tau, 0-12 h after drug administration, AUC tau) were between 0.7 +/- 0.3 ng/ml and 5.6 +/- 2.9 ng/ml and 2.4 +/- 1.3 h.ng/ml and 20.4 +/- 14.0 h.ng/ml, respectively, indicating dose-proportional PK of tegaserod in the range 2-12 mg b.i.d.
Title: Multiple-dose pharmacokinetics confirm no accumulation and dose proportionality of the novel promotile drug tegaserod (HTF 919).
Name: Tegaserod

Sentece: Small bowel, ascending colon half-life (in pharmacokinetics) (t1/2), and colonic geometric centre (8, 24, 48 h) were assessed by scintigraphy.
